snippet.title: Hatsune Miku Tycoon Introduction
snippet.description:
Play cards with Miku & friends! 
Play Tycoon with Hatsune Miku themed playing cards! There are a total of 27 varieties of cards to choose from. 
"Multiplayer available! 
Connect with friends nearby via Bluetooth to play together! 
You can send stickers to each other while you play! "

■Smartphone game app 
"Hatsune Miku Tycoon" now available for iOS and Android! 
・App Store：https://apps.apple.com/app/id1561931022
・Google Play：https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.crypton.match
■Free to play 
■Genre: card game 
■Mobile Contents Team Official Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/cfm_mobile
